paragraphs.title: Path to purchase
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)
select 
   p.category
from
  clickstream.purchased_sessions s
  left outer join clickstream.products p on s.url = p.url
where
  s.url not like '%/product/%' and s.url != '/'

paragraphs.title: Page abandonment report
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)
SELECT url FROM
   (SELECT *, RANK() over (partition by swid order by id desc) as rank FROM clickstream.weblogs) weblogs
where swid not in (select distinct swid from clickstream.purchased_sessions) and rank=1 and purchase_flag!=1

paragraphs.title: Gender and age distribution for visits
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)
select gender,age from 
  (select distinct(swid) from clickstream.weblogs) a 
join 
  (select swid, gender_cd gender, CAST(datediff(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()), from_unixtime(unix_timestamp(birth_dt,'dd-MMM-yy'))) / 365  AS INT) age from clickstream.users where gender_cd!='U') b
on 
  a.swid = b.swid

paragraphs.title: Problem pages (with error codes)
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)
select url from clickstream.weblogs where error_flag=1
